data.description:
Welcome to this stunning three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom residence nestled in the sought-after community of Torino.This residence has undergone a series of remarkable upgrades, boasting a contemporary aesthetic and enhanced functionality. The kitchen has been transformed with pristine white quartz countertops, complemented by brand-new 2023 appliances, providing a sleek and modern culinary space for both cooking enthusiasts and entertainers alike.Step onto the vinyl wood flooring that graces the entire home, offering durability, style, and easy maintenance. The remodeled bathrooms showcase sophisticated upgrades, exuding elegance and offering a luxurious retreat within your own home. Moreover, the property features a brand-new HVAC system installed in 2023, ensuring optimal comfort and efficiency throughout the seasons. The thoughtful upgrades and meticulous attention to detail make this home a standout choice for those seeking modernity and comfort.

Outside, the landscape embodies serenity, providing a tranquil backdrop for outdoor activities and relaxation.

Schedule a viewing today to experience the epitome of refined living!
